---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'

import SocialIcons from './SocialIcons.astro'


const {fullName, title, institute, profilePicture} = Astro.props
---
<div class='flex-1'>
  <h1 class='text-3xl font-bold mb-2'>
    Welcome! I'm <span class='text-secondary'>{fullName}</span>
  </h1>
  <p class='text-xl text-gray-600 mb-4'>{title}{institute ? ` at ${institute}` : ''}</p>
  
  <p class="text-lg mb-2 text-justify">
  I am an Indian-born bioinformatics scientist with a decade of experience in analyzing next-generation sequencing data, particularly from human cancer studies. Holding a PhD from the University of Virginia, I specialize in developing computational tools to unravel the complexities of genomic data to advance translational research. Driven by a passion for the intersection of data science and biology, I am dedicated to advancing personalized cancer treatments through the power of computational biology.
</p>

<p class="text-lg mb-2 text-justify">
  <em>To learn more about my journey to the USA and how my experiences have shaped my career, check out this 
  <a href="https://youtu.be/_s2hSEvTda4?feature=shared" target="_blank" 
     style="text-decoration: underline; color: blue; font-style: italic;">
    video
  </a> I recorded with a close friend, where I share the milestones and challenges of my path in science.</em>
</p>

<p class="text-lg mb-2 text-justify">
  I am also currently volunteering as a web page developer for 
  <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/groups/13074137/" target="_blank" 
     style="text-decoration: underline; color: blue; font-style: italic;">
    Boston-area Women in Bioinformatics
  </a>, contributing to the development of their online presence.
</p>

<p class="text-lg mb-2 text-justify">
  When I am not diving into the data, I enjoy hiking with my family, tending to my garden, photography, and tapping into my creative side by painting mandalas!
</p>


  {/*
  <div class='flex gap-4'>
    <SocialIcons />
  </div>
  */}

</div>
<div class='size-72 lg:block hidden'>
  <!-- Add your profile image -->
  <Image
    src={profilePicture}
    alt={fullName}
    class='w-full h-full mask mask-circle size-44'
  />
</div>